subSubSection.paragraph:
This species is similar to 
Proiectus thunbergis
Xue, Song, Amrine & Hong, 2007, but can be differentiated from the latter by median and admedian lines of prodorsal shield simple (median and admedian lines with granules in 
Proiectus thunbergis
), opisthosoma dorsally annuli with weak filamentous microtubercles (opisthosoma dorsally annuli with round microtubercles in 
Proiectus thunbergis
), tarsal empodium (em) 5-rayed (4-rayed in 
Proiectus thunbergis
).
